Philip Falcone ’s wireless-spectrum
company, LightSquared Inc., asked a bankruptcy court to halt for
60 days a lawsuit that his investment firm, Harbinger Capital
Partners LLC, brought against the GPS industry, saying it
overlaps with issues raised in the LightSquared bankruptcy case.  To contact the reporter on this story:
